MobileReceiptLineCommentActionForm is an ActionForm
    action is MobileCreate
    use for smartphone
    title is "CreateComment"
    Layout
        two column table
            column1
                CommentTitle
                    label is "Title"
            column2
                Attachment.File
                    label is "Attachment"
        two column table
            column1 of 50%
                TransientPrintOnInternalDocuments
                TransientPrintOnDeliveryTicket
            column2 of 50%
                TransientPrintOnReceivingDocument
                TransientInvoiceComments
        single column
            CommentText
                label is "Comment"
                use text area of 8 lines
